+ * Rutas resultantes:
+ *   TC-02: {closingDayPath}/{storeCode}/{transferFolder}/{file}.zip
+ *          â {closingDayPath}/{storeCode}/{processedFolder}/{file}.zip
+ *   TC-03: {journalPath}/{storeCode}/{file}.zip  (descarga y elimina)
